data.description: Welcome Home to a Rare and Amazing opportunity in the wonderful Quail Lakes Neighborhood. A beautiful, well maintained 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath home features a living room and dining room with unobstructed lake views.  Enjoy a perfectly situated kitchen adjacent to a family/media room.  One powder room (half bath) located on ground floor, one bedroom, one full bathroom and one primary bedroom with ensuite bath located on second floor. Wood, plantation shutters throughout; several pane windows flood the home with natural lighting.  Home has an attached 2-car garage, a charming private courtyard and a small dock off the back patio.  Sunsets are calling! (Photos supplied by seller at seller request.)
